**`tests/comments.test.ts` expects exactly 2 comments on post 1.** The seed data in `src/db.ts` has 2 comments with `postId: 1` (IDs 1 and 2). No existing test adds comments to post 1 without auth, so guarding `POST /posts/:postId/comments` with `authenticate` will not break those counts as long as the auth test suite's `beforeAll` doesn't fail silently.

